<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This chapter may be cited as the “Death on the High Seas Act”.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf6a0ae14-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/304/s6/c">Pub. L. 109–304, § 6(c)</ref>, <date date="2006-10-06">Oct. 6, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1511">120 Stat. 1511</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
